*   **Presenter:** Luis M. Contreras
*   **Slides:** [05 IETF Network Slice Application in 3GPP 5G End-to-End](https://datatracker.ietf.org/meeting/126/materials/slides-126-teas-sessb-05-ietf-network-slice-application-in-3gpp-5g-end-to-end-00)
*   **Draft:** `draft-ietf-teas-5g-network-slice-application`
*   **Discussion:**
    *   Version 07 addresses 3GPP SA2 Liaison Statement 2006. Changes include aligning terminology with 3GPP definitions, adjusting slice identifiers, and adding details on mapping processes between 3GPP management systems and the IETF Network Slice Controller (NSC).
